precis:
Enactment of the NOVA SCOTIA OFFSHORE PETROLEUM INSTALLATIONS REGULATIONS
which establish minimum safety requirements which must be met by all
persons engaged in the exploration, development and production of oil and
gas in the Nova Scotia offshore area.
